{
  "id": "RAW_963fab",
  "title": "“Qwen3 之后，我才真正敢投 AI 应用”",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/v6DeSAHngj_yd8mpfxIZbA",
  "date": "2025-05-01 01:00:47",
  "author": "Yoky",
  "siteName": "硅星人Pro",
  "content": "\n \n \n  <section style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 30px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;background:none;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n    <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/21edca28-b3ad-4e76-9e79-94a40a7feb00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"562\" data-imgfileid=\"100128889\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/21edca28-b3ad-4e76-9e79-94a40a7feb00/public\">\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 15px 0px 0px;letter-spacing: inherit;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);font-size: 13px;line-height: 21px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\">作者</span><i style=\"letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:12px;font-style:normal;\"><span leaf=\"\">｜</span></i><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">Yoky</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">邮箱</span><i style=\"letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:12px;font-style:normal;\"><span leaf=\"\">｜</span></i><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">yokyliu@pingwest.com</span></span>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">2025年4月29日凌晨，距离</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">通义千问</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">Qwen3正式发布还有5小时，X和GitHub上的开发者们已经搬好小板凳蹲守发布。开源社区的技术爱好者们熬夜刷新，等待第一时间测试和体验这款备受期待的中国大模型新作。</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">甚至中国开发者已经蹲守通宵，在发布凌晨5点发布的第一时间测试并发布了评测报告。</span></span></b><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">这样的现象曾经只在OpenAI发布新模型前出现过如此关注度。如今，中国大模型也能引发全球开发者如此热切的期待，不仅是模型技术的突破，也是因为对于开发者和企业而言，能够真正用起来，产生产业价值。</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">“在为企业在国内选模型，基本上只有Qwen和DeepSeek两个选项，但R1参数太大了，很多场景不需要那么强的性能。对比来看，千问系列提供了从小到大全系列参数规模的选择，在任何场景下都能找到适合的模型。”</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">Agent数字员工应用公司</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">语核科技创始人翟星吉告诉我们。</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">尤其在Qwen3发布之后，模型尺寸从0.6B到235B再度拓宽</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">光谱</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">，并且进一步降低了部署和推理成本之后，企业和开发者的门槛再度被磨平，也为应用生态的爆发奠定了基础。</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">“Qwen3以后，我才真正敢投大模型应用。”一位投资人对硅星人坦白：“端侧算力不足是事实，如果一味用云端模型没法本地部署，很多功能被限制用户也会担心隐私的问题。”</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">大模型竞赛的第一赛段已经过去，淘金之后企业和开发者能够选择有足够性能的模型其实并不多，而Qwen似乎已经成为了中国环境的首选。</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"></span></p>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">\n   <section style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;letter-spacing: inherit;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px -30px;padding: 0px;hyphens: auto;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 16px;color: transparent;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;width: 30px;height: 30px;border-radius: 50%;background: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">1</span></p>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px 0px 24px;margin:0px 0px 0px 15px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:20px;line-height:1.75em;hyphens:auto;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;font-weight: bold;letter-spacing: inherit;color: rgb(55, 80, 114);\"><span leaf=\"\">以服务产业为目标做模型</span></strong></p>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">回顾Qwen系列模型的发展历程，能够发现其与其他大模型的核心区别：</span></span><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">不是单纯追求技术领先，而是以服务产业实际需求为</span></span></b><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">导向。</span></span></b><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">做“精”还是做“全”，DeepSeek和Qwen代表着这两个技术的方向。</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">Qwen系列模型以“全谱系”布局策略，为不同场景提供针对性解决方案。从参数规模来看，Qwen</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">3</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">涵盖从轻量级的0.6B、1.7B、4B、8B、14B、32B稠密模型，到30B-A3B和235B-A22B的混合专家模型，覆盖了从端侧到云端的所有部署需求。在模型类型上，</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">更大的</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">Qwen</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">系列</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">不仅有基础语言模型，还包括推理模型、多模态视觉理解(VLM)、图像生成、视频理解等全模态能力。</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">翟星吉指出：</span></span><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">“它的模型系列覆盖的很全，从文本到VL多模态识别，再到推理模型，你会发现全套它都有。它很早就探索了</span></span></b><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">Q</span></span></b><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">VQ</span></span></b><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">，就是视觉推理模型。”</span></span></b><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">这种全谱系布局使得各类企业都能找到适合自己场景的模型。例如，儿童智能玩具创业公司跃然创新创始人李勇告诉我们：“之前受限于芯片性能、成本和功耗，无法在端侧部署推理模型。但Qwen</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">3-</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">0.6B的推出让端侧部署成为可能，端侧部署意味着无需联网，解决了隐私问题，同时消除了网络限制和Token计费成本。”</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">更广泛的应用场景看，Qwen为各类终端设备提供了精准匹配的解决方案：0.6B和1.7B模型支持开发者用于推测性解码和</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">小终端部署</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">；4B模型</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">适合</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">手机端侧应用优化；8B模型</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">可</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">针</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">对电脑或智能汽车座舱场景设计；14B模型适合普通开发者和中小企业使用，资源需求适中；32B模型是企业最喜欢的规模，支持大规模商业部署；MoE模型则为追求极致性能的场景提供服务。</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">翟星吉解释道：“你像我们给客户部署，如果要推理模型，我肯定会考虑大部分客户资源情况，</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">很多人会选择基于千问32B的流量版本的推理模型，或者直接用QWQ</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">-</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">32B。”</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">相比之下，Llama比Qwen更早开源，但却在后续的发展中逐渐成为了开源的第二选择。首先其在参数规模选择上存在明显短板。Llama的大模型如400B-500B参数规模对企业而言难以部署，需要庞大的计算资源；而70B参数的模型又被开发者普遍认为能力不足。</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">相比之下，千问72B被认为刚好达到了企业能负担的最大参数规模，在性能和成本之间取得了平衡。另一位开发者解释道：“我们测算下来，企业最多就是部署72B的模型，再大就部署不了了。”</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">其次，Llama在多语言特别是中文能力上明显不足。“中文语境下，Llama语料数据比较少，它只有5%的多语种数据，95%的英语语种数据。所以大家会觉得它在中文场景下有点笨。”这导致Llama在全球化应用场景中的适应性不佳，尤其对中文开发者而言，其实用价值大打折扣。</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">这种策略的成功体现在Qwen在开源社区获得的广泛认可上：全球衍生模型数量已超过10万，下载量超过3亿，在HuggingFace社区2024年全球模型下载量中占比超30%。在2025年2月的Huggingface全球开源大模型榜单中，排名前十的开源模型全部都基于Qwen二次开发。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">\n   <section style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;letter-spacing: inherit;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px -30px;padding: 0px;hyphens: auto;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 16px;color: transparent;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;width: 30px;height: 30px;border-radius: 50%;background: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">1</span></p>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px 0px 24px;margin:0px 0px 0px 15px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:20px;line-height:1.75em;hyphens:auto;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;font-weight: bold;letter-spacing: inherit;color: rgb(55, 80, 114);\"><span leaf=\"\">为预训练Agent，提供BaseModel</span></strong></p>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">“现在一个Agent不开出多模态的话，肯定是没有前途的。”上述投资人讲道：“在当前阶段，构建智能Agent需要模型具备强大的多模态理解能力、推理能力和自主决策能力。”</span></span><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">当Agent俨然已经成为了下一代应用的核心，而构建高效Agent需要强大的底层模型支持。</span></span></b><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">有了在制造业深耕Agent的诸多尝试后，翟星吉认为现在到了一个Agent的关键节点，“我们现在做的Agent，比如像Manus</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">背后肯定还是有手搭的workflow</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果尝试不再是固定流程的，它是智能判断的</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">，</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">我需要找这个人干什么，我需要下单，我需要找这个人验证，我需要取消，那在这场景下，就需要基于一个强大的base model做预训练的Agent模型。”</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">“首先</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">它</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">应该</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">是一个推理模型，这是基础的。然后在推理模型上去做再训练，把整个任务的第一步、第二步、第三步的路径数据，以及在每一步的思考数据，为什么要这么做的思考数据，以及最终的结果数据全部标出来，标出来之后用强化学习的方式让它不停地去迭代。”</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">这种训练方法本质上是教会模型如何进行任务分解、如何思考以及如何利用工具，而千问作为基础模型提供了强大的语言理解能力和逻辑推理框架。翟星吉进一步补充：“我们到现在都是自己写推理模板，让大模型去按照这个推理模板一步一步走，但未来</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">希望</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">Agent</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">一步到位就出来推理模板，不需要我们去提供了，它自己会思考，自己会形成一个推理的架构和路径模板，这对基础模型的能力要求很高。”</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">Qwen3的混合推理能力，为Agent开发提供了更灵活的思考与决策框架。在推理模式下，模型会执行更多中间步骤，而在非推理模式下，模型则可快速遵循指令生成答案。这种能力与人类思维极为相似：对简单问题快速作答，面对复杂问题则深思熟虑。在开发智能Agent时，这种混合推理能力显得尤为重要。</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">千问还进一步通过Qwen-Agent与MCP（Model-as-Copilot Platform）的结合降低了开发门槛，这一创新举措使得开发者能够以更低成本快速构建智能应用。传统的Agent开发需要专业的AI工程师和大量资源投入，而Qwen-Agent框架与MCP平台的结合，创造了一种'低代码'的Agent开发模式。开发者只需定义任务流和工具集，系统会自动处理复杂的推理过程和执行路径。这种方式极大地简化了开发流程，使得没有深厚AI背景的普通开发者也能构建功能强大的智能应用。</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">MCP平台作为Agent的运行环境，提供了工具调用、权限管理、数据处理等基础设施，而Qwen-Agent则专注于智能决策和推理能力。以前构建一个能处理客户服务的Agent，可能需要1-2个月的开发周期和专业AI团队。现在通过Qwen-Agent与MCP的结合，一个普通开发者可能只需1-2周就能完成原型开发，实现更高质量的交互体验。</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">这种降低门槛的方式使得AI应用开发呈现“平民化”趋势，让更多中小企业和个人开发者也能参与智能应用创新，才能带来应用的爆发。</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"></span></p>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">\n   <section style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;letter-spacing: inherit;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px -30px;padding: 0px;hyphens: auto;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 16px;color: transparent;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;width: 30px;height: 30px;border-radius: 50%;background: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">1</span></p>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px 0px 24px;margin:0px 0px 0px 15px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:20px;line-height:1.75em;hyphens:auto;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;font-weight: bold;letter-spacing: inherit;color: rgb(55, 80, 114);\"><span leaf=\"\">开源不是口号，是“生存方式”</span></strong></p>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">如今的一切开放，其实是建立在真开源的基础上。</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">“Qwen是真的很大方，最好性能的模型都拿来开源</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">。”翟星吉感叹道。</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">从最小的0.6B到最大的72B，再到新一代的235B MoE模型，所有规格都对外开源；不保留最好的模型作为闭源产品，而是将每个级别最好的模型完整开源；持续更新迭代，不断推出新的模型和能力，从文本到多模态，从对话到推理的全方位开放。</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">不是保留最好的模型作为闭源产品，而是将每个级别最好的模型完整开源。</span></span></b><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">事实上，基座模型厂商通常开源性能有限的小模型，将高性能大模型保留为付费API服务，从而形成完整的商业闭环，才是行业常见的开源模式。</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">而Qwen全部尺寸模型向社区开放，没有任何能力衰减或功能限制，不只是预训练模型，还包括SFT微调版本、对话版本和各种专业领域的指令优化模型，为开发者提供了即取即用的解决方案，同时允许开发者进行深度修改和二次开发，而不是像某些厂商那样只提供有限访问权限的“半开源”模式。这种无保留的开放态度，已经不再是开源战略，而是生存之本。</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">“到2024年年中多模态模型开始逐步成熟之后，千问是最开始推VL模型的，从千问2.0就开始有多模态模型，然后2.5的多模态更强了。而Llama3.2才支持图像识别，已经晚了”。翟星吉回忆到，Qwen团队“太卷了”。</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">模型的开放与云的服务形成了良好的闭环。阿里云作为国内第一的云厂商，需要有更多客户在上面调用，提供MaaS服务。当它将开源生态做起来以后，养成了品牌心智，如果需要闭源模型，自然也会选择千问。</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">另一位to B领域的创业者讲道：“如果我们现在在国内去做应用，能用云，我们一定优先用云，没有运维成本，没有部署成本。但如果客户一定要私有化，那我们就会选择开源模型部署，尤其是在一些特殊行业，如金融、政府和医疗领域，出于数据安全和合规要求，往往需要完全私有化部署。”</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">在全球范围内，目前模型和云能够形成良性闭环的，也就只有阿里一家。微软选择与OpenAI合作提供服务，AWS选择与Anthropic合作。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">从技术到产业，从研究到应用，Qwen系列通过全面开源的策略，不仅赢得了开发者的青睐，也在实际商业环境中找到了自己的位置。开源不只是分享代码，它是构建生态的方式，是连接开发者和企业的桥梁，更是在激烈的大模型竞争中生存和发展的根本。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n \n",
  "aiSummary": "Qwen3 大模型的全谱系布局、产业导向设计和开源策略为 AI 应用开发提供了广泛选择，显著降低了企业和开发者的使用门槛，并在中文语境下展现出独特优势",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Qwen3 大模型的全谱系布局、产业导向设计和开源策略为 AI 应用开发提供了广泛选择，显著降低了企业和开发者的使用门槛，并在中文语境下展现出独特优势",
  "summary": "文章详细介绍了通义千问 Qwen3 大模型的特点及其对 AI 应用生态的影响。Qwen3 以服务产业实际需求为导向，通过提供从 0.6B 到 235B 的全谱系模型选择，满足了从端侧到云端的不同部署需求，特别在中文语境下展现出显著优势。文章特别强调了 Qwen3 的开源策略，认为其无保留的开放态度促进了 AI 应用的创新和发展。多位行业专家和开发者分享了 Qwen3 在实际应用中的优势，包括多模态能力、推理性能和部署灵活性，并与 Llama 等国际模型进行了对比。文章还探讨了 Qwen3 对智能 Agent 开发的推动作用，以及其与阿里云服务形成的良性商业闭环。",
